</div>
<div>
<p>
<measure quantity="2" unit="months">
<num value="2">二</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>秦賊據魏潼關<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>
<num value="57">庚申</num>
<pc>，</pc>魏東郡民趙<date notBefore="954" notAfter="960">顯德</date>反<pc>，</pc>殺太守裴煙<pc>，</pc>自號都督<pc>。</pc>
