<div>
<p>夏<pc>，</pc>
<measure quantity="4" unit="months">
<num value="4">四</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>魏將元斌之討東郡<pc>，</pc>斬趙<date notBefore="954" notAfter="960">顯德</date>
<pc>。</pc>
